name: Dewi Lanjar
shortLoreBlurb: Dewi Lanjar is a deity/spirit from Java/Indonesia tied to north coast sea queen, wealth. Appeased for safe travel and rains.
overlapsLinks: Caishen (Chinese), Fortuna (Roman), Lakshmi (Hindu), Naga (India/SE Asia), Poseidon (Greek), Tangaroa (Polynesia), Yemaya (Yoruba)
